data.description: Beautiful 1-story fully renovated with no expense spared! This home is the perfect space for family and friends to gather. The interior is fresh and new with tasteful finishes that create a warm and welcoming ambiance. The open kitchen boasts ample cabinetry and granite-like counters. This home has been renovated with comfort and style in mind to create a cohesive and inviting space. Outside, you'll find a large backyard with plenty of room to play, relax, and entertain. This peaceful neighborhood has minimal traffic, friendly neighbors and no HOA. Solar panels convey with the home and help significantly reduce the electricity bill! Seller is willing to pay off solar panels with an acceptable offer. Schedule your showing today!
